JOHANNESBURG – The Super Bowl has come and gone and while South Africans might not be American football crazy, we certainly know how to appreciate amazing adverts. Companies in the United States brought out the big guns and big budgets as they jumped onto the Super Bowl bandwagon. Squarespace - Keanu Reeves Doritos – Morgan Freeman and Peter Dinklage, featuring Missy Elliott and Busta Rhymes Kia Motors - Steven Tyler Lexus - Black Panther Pepsi – cameo appearances by Britney Spears, Cindy Crawford and even Michael Jackson eNCA